[[Saint Lucia]] requires its residents to register their [[motor vehicle]]s and display '''[[vehicle registration plate]]s'''.<ref>http://www.worldlicenseplates.com/world/CA_STLU.html</ref> Current plates are [[Vehicle_registration_plates_of_the_United_States#Designs_and_serial_formats|North American standard]] 6 × 12 inches (152 × 300 mm). Older license plates are owner provided and come in different styles.<ref>http://www.plateshack.com/y2k/St_Lucia/stluciay2k.htm</ref>
